OL,3,CWoman says boyfriend stalked her for a
OL,4,Cyear before she sought help
OL,6,F"He would send lovely loving messages
OL,7,Fand then when you don't respond, the
OL,8,Fnext day, you'd get vile messages
OL,9,Fcalling me all sorts of names accusing
OL,10,Fme of doing horrific things."
OL,12,F"I went to dinner one night, I found
OL,13,Fhim standing next to my car in the
OL,14,Fpouring rain."
OL,16,FHe send messages trying to guess where
OL,17,Fshe was then turned up at her new home.
OL,19,F"The doorbell went and it was him
OL,20,Foutside and it was terrifying."
