OL,3,CWoman says boyfriend stalked her for a
OL,4,Cyear before she sought help
OL,6,FShe phoned the Police and hid in the
OL,7,Fkitchen. It was only then that she
OL,8,Frealised she was a victim of stalking.
OL,10,F"You think of stalking as being a man
OL,11,Fin a bush or hiding behind net
OL,12,Fcurtains and I didn't expect someone I
OL,13,Floved to do this to me."
OL,15,FHe was issued with a restraining order
OL,16,Ffor a year but the stalking continued.
OL,18,F'Sarah' is now trying to rebuild her
OL,19,Flife and she'd like her stalker to get
OL,20,Fthe help he needs so that he can get
OL,21,Fon with his life.
