OL,3,CWoman says boyfriend stalked her for a
OL,4,Cyear before she sought help
OL,6,F"I mistook it for love. I mistook it
OL,7,Ffor not being able to let me go
OL,8,Fbecause we had a good thing. But it's
OL,9,Fnot."
OL,11,F"It went on and on, and even though I
OL,12,Fsaid stop, I'm not coming back, he
OL,13,Fcarried on."
OL,15,FDetective Sergeant Kerri Bartup works
OL,16,Fwith Sussex Police's Complex Domestic
OL,17,FAbuse and Stalking Unit, she says it
OL,18,Fcan be difficult to recognise.
